FC's Stewart Robson and Shaka Hislop discuss Chelsea's tactics in their 2-0 win over Liverpool.

Twenty-four hours on from Chelsea’s headline-grabbing 2-0 defeat of Liverpool at Anfield and the vitriolic diatribes lambasting the manner in which Jose Mourinho achieved victory continue to smother every form of media to the point of boredom.

Everton kept pace with Arsenal in the race for the Premier League's top four with a comprehensive 2-0 victory at home to Manchester United on Sunday in David Moyes' return to Goodison Park.

After Bayern Munich's 4-0 loss to Real Madrid, the ESPN FC team give their take on Bayern's defensive struggles and lacking offense.


